programme.title: La maldicion del ro
programme.desc: Un etologo que realizaba trabajo de campo queda atrapado al otro lado del ro, donde se encuentra con un pueblo abandonado.

programme.title: La noche del traidor
programme.desc: Un antiguo grupo de la Resistencia francesa vuelve a reunirse una decada despues de la Segunda Guerra Mundial para acabar con el topo que haba entre ellos, el que traiciono a su antiguo lder y lo llevo a la perdicion.

programme.title: Rer o morir
programme.desc: Un grupo de comicos prisioneros en un campo de detencion se enfrenta a un cruel desafo. Si no hacen rer a un general alemn, sern ejecutados.

programme.title: Obsesionada
programme.desc: Sophie Delalande esconde una herida que nunca se ha cerrado, su hija Hortense fue secuestrada cuando tena tres aos. Un da, Sophie cree reconocer a su hija desaparecida en la figura de una joven veinteaera.

programme.title: Fuera de lmites
programme.desc: Un inquilino se niega a abandonar su apartamento en un barrio que se est gentrificando. Su empeo en seguir viviendo en el mismo lugar lo enfrenta de manera violenta a los inversores inmobiliarios y a las autoridades.

programme.title: Le Horla
programme.desc: Damien y Nadia abandonan Pars con su hija, Chloe. Se instalan a orillas del ro Cher y comienzan una nueva vida. Desde el principio, Damien oye ruidos que parecen atravesar las paredes. Detrs de este nuevo inicio se esconde una amenaza secreta.

programme.title: Sin lmite
programme.desc: Un mecnico de 30 aos al borde de la quiebra acude al banco a pedir un prestamo, pero en un abrir y cerrar de ojos se ve envuelto en un robo, con la polica y el hampa pisndole los talones, y con un rehen improbable.

programme.title: Corazones de Bali
programme.desc: Despues de la muerte de su abuela, una influencer convence a su madre y a su hermana de acompaarla a Bali para descubrir la historia de su familia.

programme.title: Sol ardiente
programme.desc: Un resort costero sufre una ola de calor abrasadora. El agua escasea, y la violencia est a punto de estallar. Un joven es el encargado de proteger la casa vaca de una familia adinerada mientras estn fuera, ante el riesgo de saqueos.

programme.title: El chef Italiano
programme.desc: Marco, un chef italiano talentoso, abandona su carrera y regresa a Italia para cuidar a su padre enfermo. All conoce a Olivia, una joven australiana llena de vida y espritu, que le dar un vuelco a su vida.

programme.title: Robin Hood
programme.desc: In twelfth-century England, Robin Longstride and his band of marauders confront corruption in a local village and lead an uprising against the crown that will forever alter the balance of power.

programme.title: Monkey Man
programme.desc: After years of suppressed rage, an underground fighter discovers a way to infiltrate the enclave of the citys sinister elite. He soon embarks on an explosive campaign of retribution to settle the score with the men who took everything from him.

programme.title: The Green Knight
programme.desc: King Arthurs headstrong nephew embarks on a daring quest to confront the Green Knight, a mysterious giant who appears at Camelot. Risking his head, he sets off on an epic adventure to prove himself before his family and court.

programme.title: Legends of the Condor Heroes: The Gallants
programme.desc: The Mongols, led by Genghis Khan, go west to destroy the Jin Dynasty, and want to go south to destroy the Song Dynasty. Martial Arts Masters from several Schools in the Central Plains of China fight gathering strength to defend Xiangyang.

programme.title: Marnie
programme.desc: A man struggles to break the thieving habits of his kleptomaniac wife and restore harmony to their marriage.

programme.title: Petite maman
programme.desc: Nelly, an 8-year-old girl, has just lost her beloved grandmother and is helping her parents clean out her mothers childhood home. One day, her mom abruptly leaves, and Nelly meets a girl her age as shes building a tree house in the woods.

programme.title: The Summit
programme.desc: During a presidential summit in Chile, Argentinas president Hernn Blanco goes through family drama affecting the relationship with his daughter while facing the most important moment in his career.

programme.title: Secretos del pasado
programme.desc: A federal agent investigates the decades-old death of a teenage girl in his drought-stricken hometown.

programme.title: State of Play
programme.desc: An investigative journalist (Russell Crowe) stumbles into a cover-up of gigantic proportions as he and his partner probe the murder of a beloved congressmans (Ben Affleck) mistress.

programme.title: Horizon: An American Saga: Chapter 1
programme.desc: In 1859 families discover the lure of the Old West as they settle in territories from Wyoming to Kansas. Meanwhile, a gruff cowboy soon finds himself on the run with a prostitute and a young boy after killing a fellow gunman.

programme.title: Steve Jobs
programme.desc: From 1984 to 1998, Apple Inc. co-founder Steve Jobs uses innovation and fierce determination to develop highly anticipated and revolutionary computers, including the Macintosh and the iMac.

programme.title: Medidas Extremas
programme.desc: A homeless mans mysterious death puts an emergency-room physician (Hugh Grant) on the trail of a doctor (Gene Hackman) who experiments on the living.

programme.title: Arrival
programme.desc: A linguistics professor (Amy Adams) leads an elite team of investigators in a race against time to communicate with extraterrestrial visitors.

programme.title: Black Bag
programme.desc: When his beloved wife, Kathryn, is suspected of betraying the nation, intelligence agent George Woodhouse faces the ultimate test -- loyalty to his marriage or his country.

programme.title: Rear Window
programme.desc: A paralyzed architect believes he has witnessed a murder in this remake of Alfred Hitchcocks 1954 classic.

programme.title: Joika
programme.desc: Joy Womack becomes one of the few Western women to be accepted to the Bolshoi Ballet Academy in Moscow.

programme.title: The Kitchen
programme.desc: Life in a NYC restaurant kitchen during the lunchtime rush showcases a blend of cultures from around the world.

programme.title: The Peasants
programme.desc: Jagna finds herself caught between the desires of a rich farmer, his eldest son and other men.

programme.title: The Color Purple
programme.desc: Torn apart from her sister and her children, Celie faces many hardships, including an abusive husband. With support from a singer and her stepdaughter, she ultimately finds extraordinary strength in the unbreakable bonds of a new kind of sisterhood.

programme.title: Priscilla
programme.desc: When teenage Priscilla Beaulieu meets Elvis Presley at a party, the man who is already a meteoric rock n roll superstar becomes someone entirely unexpected in private moments: a thrilling crush, an ally in loneliness, a vulnerable best friend.

programme.title: Between the Temples
programme.desc: A cantor in a crisis of faith finds his world turned upside down when his grade school music teacher reenters his life as his new adult bat mitzvah student.

programme.title: Demolition
programme.desc: A sympathetic woman (Naomi Watts) and her young son (Judah Lewis) form a strong bond with an investment banker (Jake Gyllenhaal) whose life begins to unravel following the death of his wife (Heather Lind).

programme.title: Jarhead
programme.desc: A Marine (Jake Gyllenhaal) and his comrades (Peter Sarsgaard, Jamie Foxx) form brotherly bonds while patrolling the Iraqi desert during the Gulf War.

programme.title: The Last Rifleman
programme.desc: World War II veteran Artie Crawford lives in a care home in Northern Ireland. After his wifes death, he decides to ignore all advice and sets off alone to France to attend the 75th anniversary of the D-Day landings.
